Awesome Python ￼

An opinionated list of awesome Python frameworks, libraries, software and resources.
Inspired by awesome-php.
	•	Awesome Python
	◦	Admin Panels
	◦	Algorithms and Design Patterns
	◦	ASGI Servers
	◦	Asynchronous Programming
	◦	Audio
